data.description: Gorgeous updated townhouse in the well located and maintained Dutch Ridge Complex.  Relax in the open living room with a wood burning fire warming the room. Enjoy cooking on a new GE Monogram Range. Updated kitchen with new hardware, fixtures, stainless appliances, granite countertops and subway tile backsplash.  New wood laminate flooring on both levels.  Updated full bath between the Master and the second bedroom.  Vaulted ceilings and sky lights in the light and airy Master bedroom.  Security system with a monitored smart door bell.  Fenced in back patio backing to HOA green space. One reserved parking spot directly in front of the unit. All well located to trails, the foothills, shopping, parks and restaurants
